Class Budget

java.lang.Object
Budget
public class Budget extends Object
A collection of Statement objects. Includes utility methods.

    • normal

      public Budget normal(double period)
      Creates a new Budget object that adjusts all of the statements to the passed in period. ex: $200/month --> $2400/year
      Parameters:
      period - - the period of the statements in the new budget
      Returns:
      a new budget in which all statements have the given period
